node.text:
💥QL Pain💥We can promote your photos in our account. Click the link in our bio for instructions: @RunningTerritory 

⁉️ Do you have pain in the side of the low back?
-
🎯 Many times the quadratus lumborum, or the "QL", can contribute to pain in this area, as palpating this deep muscle can be very sensitive in some individuals
-
📌 This muscle connects from the top/back of the pelvis (iliac crest) to the 12th rib (the lowest one), as well as the transverse processes of the lumbar spine vertebrae (side projections of the low back bones)
-
🤸🏻 Its function is to extend (arch backward) and side bend the spine and can also act as a stabilizer, resisting side bending into the opposite direction as well as spinal flexion (forward bending)
-
🚨 If you have pain in this region, a combination of stretching and strengthening is often helpful
-
🎥 Here are some exercises that may help:
-
1️⃣ Spinal Side Bending at Door
2️⃣ Supine Lumbar Rotation
3️⃣ Sidelying Lumbar Rotation
4️⃣ Single Leg Bridge
5️⃣ Side Plank
6️⃣ Suitcase Carries
-
🚨 Remember, these are simply examples of exercises that MAY help. If you need a specific exercise program tailored to your specific situation, you should schedule a consult with the physical therapist you trust!
-
🙏🏼 I hope that was helpful!

📽 @dr.caleb.burgess

20 MIN CORE/CARDIO 🔥💦 Apply to promote your content in our account, go to our link in bio: @RunningTerritory

( like + save to try later 🏷)

No gym needed, just your mind and body. Progress needs perseverance, leave your self-doubt in the past and just focus on giving it your best right now — let’s go!!!🔻

✔️ Run 400 meters and perform each exercise for 30 seconds. Repeat this for 20 minutes with minimal to no rest. (📹: @evolve.nation)

by @everygotdamndre 💪 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @RunningTerritory.

“Is it possible that I developed this personality through fitness ?? I feel like I did 🙃🙃 or maybe my football years! 

Being dedicated to completing the tasks and not complaining about the process. Just simply being addicted to the grind and the idea of becoming who I was created to be. 

Always understand that leaving out dedication and adding in complaints will complicate things !!!

✅🔥LEGBLAST 

⚡️Jump lunge snatch 
My knees are fine thank you lol 
⚡️SS Press 
⚡️side plank thrust holds 😒 sucks” ~ Follow him for more.

node.text:
Would you dare to walk on this Via Ferrata? 😳 Share your posts with us and we will share them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @RunningTerritory 

The new Signora Delle Acque, in the Ruzza river, is a highly emotional and spectacular via ferrata that gives you unforgettable emotions; the sight embraces whole Trentino, but keeping fixed on the track too.

📽 @niklaskoessel
📍Trentino, Italy

CrusHIIT Full Body 🤩 We can share your content in our page, check the link in our bio: @RunningTerritory to follow the process.

Tell me about your favorite vacation spot 🏝

SAVE + LIKE + SHARE + CRUSH IT 👊🏼

I personally would love a few days off 😅. It’s been so busy with upcoming projects, so right about now, swimming in the ocean and chilling under an umbrella with a cold drink, somewhere tropical, sounds dreamy. Soon, soon hopefully 🙏🏻

Workout deets: 45 secs ON 15 secs OFF (beginners modify as necessary and start with 15-30 secs then rest for 45-30 secs): 3-4 rounds

📽 @senada.greca
